        <Parent_String>perfume bottles [300197635], containers for personal grooming and hygiene [300197583], containers for personal use [300198399], containers by function or context [300197200], containers (receptacles) [300197197], Containers (hierarchy name) [300045611], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
